To consume the rest service

1. GET -> http://localhost:8080/camel/rest

2. POST -> http://localhost:8080/camel/rest

{"name":"RAMANA"}



COMPONENTS SUPPORTING REST DSL

The following Camel components supports the Rest DSL:

camel-rest required contains the base rest component needed by Rest DSL

camel-netty-http

camel-jetty

camel-platform-http

camel-servlet

camel-undertow


